FIND THE FACTORIAL OF A NUMBER:
Given number=7

KEY:
* The key here is store the value of n in a variable which is initialized by 1 and multiply both.
eg: i=i*n
i is 1
n is 7 (given value)
n-- is the update expression
first iteration i value will be 1*7=7
next iteration i value will be 7*6=42
next iteration i value will be 42*5=210 and so on until n>=1.

PROGRAM:

class Factorial
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
     int n=7;
     int fact=1;
     for(;n>=1;n--)
     {
      fact=fact*n;
     }
    System.out.println(fact);
    }
}

OUTPUT:
5040
